projects.title: Custom RL Overlay
projects.description: A dynamic streaming overlay for Rocket League Esports matches, designed to read and seamlessly display in-game data. It also includes a caster panel for easy adjustment of match information.

projects.title: Swagger for AAS
projects.description: Reads data from Asset Administration Shells, generalizes it, and generates a comprehensive Swagger UI documentation to ensure clarity and accessibility for developers.

projects.title: Multi Agent System
projects.description: A Multi-Agent System for playing poker, where each CPU player acts as an agent, calculating moves using a combination of case-based reasoning and plan-based strategies for optimal gameplay.

projects.title: Scripting Language
projects.description: sQeeZ is a modern scripting language that combines simplicity, power, and flexibility. Its concise syntax enables developers to create clean, efficient code and implement complex functionalities with ease.

projects.title: Explainable CBR
projects.description: A Case-Based Reasoning (CBR) system for Minesweeper that analyzes game patterns and offers tips based on previously solved cases, enabling users to learn and improve their gameplay.

projects.title: Taxi Trips Analysis
projects.description: Analyzes NYC taxi trip data to calculate the geographic center, explore tipping behavior across districts, and highlight key areas like airports with insights into tourist and local trends.

projects.title: Webmaster MVB
projects.description: A website for a local music club, where we design and display news, manage email communication, and handle various online tasks to keep the community informed and engaged.

projects.title: Discord Bots
projects.description: Commissioned Discord bots designed to manage temporary voice channels based on user roles, handle role assignments, and automate the process of filling in form data into a document file.
